span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以我地要做嘅係推高《乜代宗師》嘅人氣，令到各大戲院（不理佢黃定藍）都將大部份嘅場次都改為《乜代宗師》！<br />\n要其他對家嘅戲連上映嘅機會都無！！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我唔夠膽講收唔收到一億，但起碼要對家仆直！"},{"pid":"68de50867c06090effa961cd2593be70af1c258c","tid":1822784,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T15:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24vLG52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24vLG52.jpg&h=10cbd100&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97222b9f0b7d8a4dc1d4cfa687dbc1fc062a4525","tid":1822784,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T15:36:40.000Z","msg":"睇，一定要睇"}]}